            "popup_content": "<h5> Kaitlynn Wheeler | Swimming </h5>\n<h6> NCAA Division I Swimmer | SEC Champion </h6>\n\n<p> A former University of Kentucky swimmer, Kaitlynn Wheeler is a multi-time All-American, SEC Champion, and NCAA qualifier. After witnessing a male swimmer dominate the women’s category at the 2022 NCAA Championships, she became a leading advocate for the integrity of women’s sports. She continues to stand up for female athletes, inspired by her sister’s own experience facing discrimination for speaking out. </p>\n\n<p> Instagram:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kaitlynnwheeler19\"> @kaitlynnwheeler19 </a></p>",
